title: Jamie XX - Untitled (Unreleased)
description: It is always the case with Jamie that when he drops something new we know that it is time to sit back, turn up the volume and embrace the genius of his creativity - this new song is no exception. With progressive vocal samples added to a sequence of synthetic harp layers, these rare 6 minutes of conciousness shifting vibes should be embraced in all their beauty to take you on a journey through your mind and soul.
